      <title>加拿大养老金计划出售西班牙不良债务组合</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/canada-pension-looking-to-sell-spanish-distressed-debt-portfolio</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大养老金计划投资委员会已将一批西班牙不良贷款组合挂牌出售，以减少其在上个十年金融危机期间对该国的风险敞口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/canada-pension-looking-to-sell-spanish-distressed-debt-portfolio</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 14:10:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前投资银行家面临 1400 万欧元德国税务丑闻罚款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/ex-london-investment-banker-finally-must-pay-bill-from-german-tax-scandal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名前伦敦投资银行家在德国首次因非法 Cum-Ex 交易被判有罪，现在必须支付法院四年多前对他判处的 1400 万欧元（1530 万美元）的罚款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/ex-london-investment-banker-finally-must-pay-bill-from-german-tax-scandal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 14:01:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>家得宝下调预期，称消费者面临压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-13/home-depot-cuts-outlook-citing-pressured-consumers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[家得宝表示，目前预计今年可比销售额将下降 3% 至 4%，而此前的预期是在线销售额和开业至少一年的门店销售额将下降 1%。这低于彭博社汇编的分析师平均预期。Dasha Afanasieva 有更多报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-13/home-depot-cuts-outlook-citing-pressured-consumers</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 13:59:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Pandora 首席执行官表示，十年后，合成钻石将比天然钻石更受欢迎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/pandora-ceo-says-diamond-market-faces-disruption-in-next-decade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Pandora A/S 的首席执行官预计，用不了 10 年，消费者购买的实验室培育钻石就会多于天然钻石，因为他们在购买珠宝时越来越多地考虑成本和气候影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/pandora-ceo-says-diamond-market-faces-disruption-in-next-decade</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 10:46:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国投资者信心跌至 1 月以来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/german-investor-confidence-plunges-to-lowest-since-january</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于一系列令人失望的数据和近期全球股市的动荡，投资者对德国经济的信心跌至一月份以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/german-investor-confidence-plunges-to-lowest-since-january</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 09:07:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
